<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM3.9.4">
<l>kalaiyilaṅku makalalku larakkarkulak koṭiyaik kātoṭumūk kuṭaṉariyak kataṟiyava ḷōṭi</l>
<l>talaiyilaṅkai vaittumalai yilaṅkaipukac ceyta taṭantōḷaṉ makiḻntiṉitu maruviyuṟai kōyil</l>
<l>cilaiyilaṅku maṇimāṭat tuccimicaic cūlañ ceḻuṅkoṇṭa lakaṭiriyac corintaceḻu muttam</l>
<l>malaiyilaṅku māḷikaimēl maliveytu nāṅkūr vaikunta viṇṇakaram vaṇaṅkumaṭa neñcē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Simple heart, worship in Vaikunta Viṇṇakaram in Nānkūr which acquires</l>
<l rend="indent">the best of fat pearls on top of palaces that shine [like] mountains,</l>
<l>Which the bellies of fat clouds pour as they flee the barbs</l>
<l rend="indent">on top of mansions with jewels shining with light,</l>
<l>The temple where dwells the broad-shouldered one,</l>
<l rend="indent">happily with affection [and] rejoicing, who made the girl of the ogre clan,</l>
<l rend="indent">with wide hips where a girdle glittered,</l>
<l>Enter into mountainous Lanka, running and screaming,</l>
<l rend="indent">clasping her lovely hands on her head</l>
<l rend="indent">when he cut off her ears and nose all at once.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
